{"tid":1155322,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞為古天奴開價：無一億唔使講！","createTime":"2019-05-15T01:06:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T09:27:32.000Z","uid":11512,"like":48,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"61a947eb92060ea66607a0c4cd8b2cc78b09ab51","tid":1155322,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:06:00.000Z","msg":"巴塞隆拿確有意出售其中場球員古天奴，但這支西甲巨人不願意低價出售只子，並已為這名巴西國腳標上1億鎊的身價。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.weserv.nl/?url=i%2Edailymail%2Eco%2Euk%2F1s%2F2019%2F05%2F14%2F09%2F13474782-0-image-a-23_1557823069217%2Ejpg&amp;w=680&amp;output=jpg&amp;q=80&amp;errorredirect=i%2Edailymail%2Eco%2Euk%2F1s%2F2019%2F05%2F14%2F09%2F13474782-0-image-a-23_1557823069217%2Ejpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.weserv.nl%2F%3Furl%3Di%252Edailymail%252Eco%252Euk%252F1s%252F2019%252F05%252F14%252F09%252F13474782-0-image-a-23_1557823069217%252Ejpg%26w%3D680%26output%3Djpg%26q%3D80%26errorredirect%3Di%252Edailymail%252Eco%252Euk%252F1s%252F2019%252F05%252F14%252F09%252F13474782-0-image-a-23_1557823069217%252Ejpg&h=4e7a3832&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現年26歲的古天奴，在去年1月以1億4500萬鎊的價錢由利物浦轉投巴塞隆拿。這名巴西中場在西甲未能踢出在紅軍時代的水準，更不時被安放在他不熟悉的邊路位置，令古天奴去意萌生。巴塞隆拿亦無意留人，但因為去季的高額投出，巴塞至少想在古天奴身上回收大半的轉會費。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.weserv.nl/?url=i%2Edailymail%2Eco%2Euk%2F1s%2F2019%2F05%2F14%2F09%2F13474792-0-image-a-25_1557823087338%2Ejpg&amp;w=680&amp;output=jpg&amp;q=80&amp;errorredirect=i%2Edailymail%2Eco%2Euk%2F1s%2F2019%2F05%2F14%2F09%2F13474792-0-image-a-25_1557823087338%2Ejpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.weserv.nl%2F%3Furl%3Di%252Edailymail%252Eco%252Euk%252F1s%252F2019%252F05%252F14%252F09%252F13474792-0-image-a-25_1557823087338%252Ejpg%26w%3D680%26output%3Djpg%26q%3D80%26errorredirect%3Di%252Edailymail%252Eco%252Euk%252F1s%252F2019%252F05%252F14%252F09%252F13474792-0-image-a-25_1557823087338%252Ejpg&h=9cc8e04e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據報道，由於轉會費高昂，基本上沒有球會願意接收這名巴西國腳，惟一有向巴塞示好的，是英超三哥車路士。據報車路士一直視古天奴為代替夏沙特的最佳人選，在來年得以進軍歐聯下，藍軍亦有充裕的資金去簽下這名巴西人。車路士方面亦準備為古天奴開出24萬鎊的周薪。不過，車路士大可能面臨轉會禁令，將在未來兩個轉會市場不得簽下新球員。而這支倫敦一哥正計劃向體育仲裁法庭上訴，成功與否，將是這宗轉會的關鍵。古天奴在巴塞的一季半間為球隊上陣了74場攻入21球，為球隊贏下了兩屆西甲冠軍。"},{"pid":"2a22ee822e7381c3df2b22ad289dae12d7895f7b","tid":1155322,"uid":11512,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zZHeUDs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzZHeUDs.gif&h=de917f19&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"adf9f0e451af3954ac2a21c8f82f86bc7612bfea","tid":1155322,"uid":165817,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"2a22ee822e7381c3df2b22ad289dae12d7895f7b","tid":1155322,"uid":11512,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zZHeUDs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzZHeUDs.gif&h=de917f19&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:08:16.000Z","msg":"仲記得佢啱啱去巴塞嗰陣 俾人串佢個嘴抽搐<br />\n而家好似好耐都冇見過佢咁笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bca5b585a216d49ba588b00cdab1b9b9acabc4c","tid":1155322,"uid":11512,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"quote":{"pid":"adf9f0e451af3954ac2a21c8f82f86bc7612bfea","tid":1155322,"uid":165817,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"2a22ee822e7381c3df2b22ad289dae12d7895f7b","tid":1155322,"uid":11512,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zZHeUDs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzZHeUDs.gif&h=de917f19&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:08:16.000Z","msg":"仲記得佢啱啱去巴塞嗰陣 俾人串佢個嘴抽搐<br />\n而家好似好耐都冇見過佢咁笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:11:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/133017_e3014a642e8